column2: select a.SystemStudentID as student_id, a.gradelevel as enrollment_grade, a.SchoolYear4Digit as schoolyear, # as period, # as assessment_subject, # as metricsource, # as metricname, sum (b.hours) as score from enrollment a join parentengagement b on a.SystemStudentID = b.SystemStudentID group by a.SystemStudentID, a.gradelevel, a.SchoolYear4Digit
